this is php cli  ,
its setup    is to print   system details and give check points  to network failures.
 we will first create a linux class  that ill do the following


1)  print os  and version
2)  print interfaces / ips
3)  print gateway
4)  Print Dns servers
4)  ping gateway
5)  ping 8.8.8.8  to test outside connectivity
6)  ping google.com  to test dns resolution
7)  test firewalls  buy  test port 443 https://google.com and port 80  http://google.com

8)  display connected devices


now make a docker file that will create an environment to test it